where_conditions: WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'amoxicillin%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')

WHERE "FLO_MEAS_NAME" LIKE ANY ('{"R JHM IP RT VENT FIO2 - PS/VS VENT","R FIO2","JHM IP RT NPPV FIO2","JHM IP RT VENT FIO2 - PCAC VENT","JHM IP RT VENT FIO2 - SIMV/VC VENT","JHM IP RT VENT FIO2 - APRV VENT","JHM IP RT VENT FIO2 - PRVC VENT","JHM IP RT VENT FIO2","JHM IP RT VENT FIO2 - SIMV/PRVC VENT","R JHM IP MEASURED FIO2","JHM IP RT VENT FIO2 - SIMV/PC VENT","JHM IP RT NPPV SET FIO2","JHM IP RT VENT FIO2 - CPAP VENT","JHM IP RT VENT FIO2 - VCAC VENT","JHM IP RT VENT FIO2 - PRVC VENT"}')

WHERE "FLO_MEAS_NAME" LIKE ANY ('{"PULSE","R ED PULSE LYING","R JHM IP PT NEW PULSE","R JHM OP OT NEW PULSE"}')
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'norepinephrine%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%injection%","%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'norepinephrine%' and "display_name" ~* 'injection' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'phenylephrine%neo-synephrine%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'meropenem%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')
WHERE "FLO_MEAS_NAME" LIKE ANY ('{"R JHM IP PT NEW BP","BLOOD PRESSURE"}')
WHERE "FLO_MEAS_NAME" LIKE ANY ('{"R JHM IP PT NEW BP","BLOOD PRESSURE"}')
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'oxacillin%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'penicillin%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'penicillin G%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'piperacillin-tazobactam%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'tobramycin%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')

WHERE "FLO_MEAS_NAME" LIKE ANY ('{"R RT VENTILATOR RESPIRATORY RATE SPONTANEOUS","R JHM IP VENT RR TOTAL CPAP/PS","R JHM IP VENT RR TOTAL APRV","R VENT RR TOTAL SIMVC","R JHM IP VENT RR TOTAL PRVC","R VENT RR TOTAL","R VENT RR TOTAL SIMV","R JHM IP VENT RR TOTAL PC/AC","R VENT RR TOTAL CPAP","R VENT RR TOTAL SIMV/PC","R JHM IP VENT RR TOTAL VCAC","R JHM IP VENT RR TOTAL PC/VS","RESPIRATIONS","R JHM IP PT NEW RESPIRATIONS","R JHM OP OT NEW RESPIRATIONS","R JHM IP VENT RR TOTAL APRV","R VENT RR TOTAL SIMVC","R JHM IP VENT RR TOTAL VCAC","R VENT RR TOTAL","R JHM IP VENT RR TOTAL PC/AC","R JHM IP VENT RR TOTAL PRVC","R VENT RR TOTAL SIMV/PC","R JHM IP VENT RR TOTAL PC/VS","R JHM IP VENT RR TOTAL CPAP/PS","R VENT RR TOTAL SIMV","R VENT RR TOTAL CPAP","RESPIRATIONS","R JHM IP PT NEW RESPIRATIONS","R JHM OP OT NEW RESPIRATIONS"}')
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'rifampin%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')
WHERE "FLO_MEAS_NAME" LIKE ANY ('{"R JHM OP OT NEW PULSE OXIMETRY","PULSE OXIMETRY"}')
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'vancomycin%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')

select_cols: "FLO_MEAS_NAME","PAT_ID" pat_id,cast("PLACEMENT_INSTANT" as timestamptz), cast("REMOVAL_DTTM" as timestamptz)

where_conditions: WHERE "diagname" ~* 'stroke' and not "diagname" ~* 'due to stroke|effect of stroke'
where diagname ~ 'UTI' or diagname ~* 'urinary tract infection|urosepsis|pyelo'
where diagname ~* 'pneumonia|acute lung injury|empyema|acute respiratory distress syndrome' or  diagname ~ 'ARDS|ALI'
where diagname ~* 'biliary sepsis|cholecystitis|ascending cholangitis|cholelithiasis|gall stones|hepatic absess|cholangitis'

where diagname ~* 'intra abdominal sepsis|abdominal catastrophe|perforated viscous|free air|pneumoperitoneum|pneumotosis|peritonitis|spontaneous bacterial peritonitis|gut translocation|c. diff|colitis|peritoneal abscess|clostridium difficile'
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'moxifloxacin%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE 'ceftriaxone%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')

where lower("NOTE_TEXT") like any ('{"% uti %"}') and not lower("NOTE_TEXT") like any ('{"%history of uti%","% ho uti%","% ro uti%","% r/o uti%","%suggestive of uti%","%hx of uti%","%uti resolved%"}')

where lower("NOTE_TEXT") like any ('{"%pneumonia%","% pna %", "% cap %","%sputum culture for afb%"}') and not lower("NOTE_TEXT") like any ('{"%history of[a-z ,]*pneumonia%","%evaluate for pneumonia%","%hx of pneumonia%","%h/o pneumonia%","%r/o [a-z ,]*pneumonia%"}')
WHERE lower("NOTE_TEXT") LIKE ANY ('{"% uti %","% urinary source%","% urinary tract infection%", "%urosepsis%","%pyelonephritis%","%pyelo %"}')
WHERE lower("NOTE_TEXT") LIKE ANY ('{"%biliary sepsis%","%cholecystitis%","%ascending cholangitis%","%cholelithiasis%","%gall stones%","%hepatic abscess%"}')

WHERE lower("NOTE_TEXT") LIKE ANY ('{"%intra abdominal sepsis%","%abdominal catastrophe%","%perforated viscous%","%free air%","%pneumoperitoneum%","%pneumotosis%","%peritonitis%","%spontaneous bacterial peritonitis%","%gut translocation%","%c.diff%","%colitis%","%peritoneal abscess%"}')
WHERE lower("NOTE_TEXT") LIKE ANY ('{"%pneumonia%","% ards %","%acute lung injury%","% ali %","%aspiration%","%empyema%"}')
WHERE lower("NOTE_TEXT") LIKE ANY ('{"%blood stream infection%","%line sepsis%","%endocarditis%"}')
WHERE lower("NOTE_TEXT") LIKE ANY ('{"%cellulitis%","%abscess%"}') and not lower("NOTE_TEXT") like any ('{"%peritoneal abscess%"}')

where lower("NOTE_TEXT") like any ('{"% ards %", "% acute respiratory distress syndrome %", "% ardsnet %"}') and not lower("NOTE_TEXT") ~ '(at risk for|evaluate for|reevaluate for|history of|h/o|ho|hx|rule out|r/o|ro|possible|resolved|suspicion of|suspicious of|suggestive of) (ards|acute respiratory distress syndrome)'
where "FLO_MEAS_NAME" ilike 'HEIGHT' and "Value" is not Null and "Value"::float between 22 and 108
where display_name ilike '%valsartan%' and display_name not ilike '%acubitril%'
WHERE "display_name" ILIKE '%norepinephrine%' AND NOT "display_name" ILIKE ANY ('{"%gel%","%vaginal%","%cream%","%ophthalmic%","%ointment%","%nebulizer%","%drop%"}')
where proc_name ilike '%blood gas%' and proc_name ilike '%arterial%' and "OrderStatus" != 'Canceled';
where "NAME" in ('GLUCOSE', 'GLUCOSE, WHOLE BLOOD','NOVA-GLUCOSE,WBLOOD','POC GLUCOSE, BLOOD')
